title: First lady aims to get more students to continue education
text: > Top News First lady aims to get more students to continue education First lady Michelle Obama speaks in the East Room of the White House in Washington, Monday, Oct. 19, 2015, unveiling a new phase of her Reach Higher initiative encouraging students to continue education after high school, a public awareness campaign and matching website to provide practical information and space to share stories, backed by more than 20 media, business and nonprofit groups. (AP Photo/Manuel Balce Ceneta)
